Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.85,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30\bord2\fnArial Black\c&HA5B7C6&\3c&HEAF7F9&}31st Annual Shuka Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:25.50,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We can blame it all on the weather
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:28.04,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,All this awkwardness and exhaustion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:32.26,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The sun hides away, pretending not to see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:35.84,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A packed train clatters along the track
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:38.22,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It brushes past a local express
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:43.39,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna search for feelings \Nin a shapeless cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:46.35,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The test asks, "How was \Nthe author feeling here?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:48.77,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What could the right answer possibly be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:53.78,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking through the script \Nof pre-established harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:59.08,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone talks about the \N"springtime of life"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:04.21,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm just not cut out for that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:09.59,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I know that this moment, \Nwhich will never come again,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:14.76,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,is rich with evanescence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:17.68,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget, ever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:20.35,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So many times before I die someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:25.27,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'll laugh thinking about what it was like
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:40.95,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like the wind's leaving me behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:46.08,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm desperately clinging on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.71,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That familiar sound of the bell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.71,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs12\fnArial Black\c&HC1B897&\3c&HE1DFDA&\fay0.12\fax-0.06\pos(420,62)}But{\c&H9882C2&}ler {\c&HC1B897&}Ca{\c&H9882C2&}fe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:51.34,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That dust piled up on the window sill
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:56.67,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Even the smell of the classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.34,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget, ever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:01.76,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So many times before I die someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:07.39,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'll laugh thinking about what it was like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:24.54,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1815,1)\c&H7F50D0&\fnImpact\fs30\pos(201.5,112)}BOCCHI THE ROCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:24.54,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1815,1)\c&H7F50D0&\fnComic Sans MS\fs26\b1\pos(464.5,272.5)}#12 Morning Light Falls on You
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.87,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:31.42,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That was our first song, \N"I Will Never Forget!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how enthusiastic they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.42,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:37.42,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:39.26,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,You were so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:42.14,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Now, before we play our next song...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:44.42,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a few words from \NKessoku Band's leader:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:46.81,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,our drummer and my senpai, Nijika Ijichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.73,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.27,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having a good time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:55.61,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,They've worked pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:56.98,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.57,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But Bocchi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.16,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Our esteemed bassist, Ryo Yamada,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:04.58,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,told me that any MCing I did for \NKessoku Band would be a flop,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and at first I thought, "How dare you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.75,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But until I learn to be \Nentertaining with this stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:11.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd stick to concert announcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:15.59,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I don't actually know \Nwhen our next concert'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:19.97,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But if you wanna see more, \Njust hit up our vocalist, Kita-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:19.97,DefaultTop,Kita's Friend A/B,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:24.43,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,or our guitarist, Bo—\NHitori Gotoh, when you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.68,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.77,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's move on to the next song!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:31.56,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.06,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Please lend us your ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.07,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Our next song is \N"To Become a Constellation..."!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:08.35,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The time's almost six
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.93,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The evening star's already out there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.44,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Walking home, stepping on shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:20.15,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping to blend into the night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.40,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:25.86,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky you, lucky you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.24,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fine this whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:30.20,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice to have everyone love you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.70,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,but now I can't get the E string in tune...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:37.63,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,"No, I've always been alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:41.63,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could become \Na constellation with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:46.59,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,On a night of falling stars, \NI make that moment's wish
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:43.97,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The E string!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.59,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But if I can at least get \Nthe B string in tune...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:53.48,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A sparkling, twinkling, \Ntrembling signal up high
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.51,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The peg's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:53.48,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,She can't use the B string now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:55.02,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,She won't be able to do her solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:57.23,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could become \Na constellation with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My solo's coming up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:01.73,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The kind that people point to in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:03.69,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If our big culture festival performance \Nfails because I had equipment trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:06.11,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let these lines \Nthat link us come undone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:04.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do, what do I do, \Nwhat do I do, what do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:11.08,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how brightly I shine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.62,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She's ad-libbing completely on the fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.71,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make sure everyone can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:24.38,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,how amazingly cool Gotoh-san really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.89,Default,Boy Student A,0000,0000,0000,,What's their guitarist doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.02,Default,Boy Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno, but it's pretty awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:36.89,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Who whips out the bottleneck \Nplaying at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:40.65,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Now it won't matter \Nif she's a little out of tune!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:46.15,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,We met each other, so far away
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:54.08,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,And because it's our karma, \Nwe'll meet again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:59.17,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,In the gaps between the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:04.67,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could become \Na constellation with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:08.80,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,As night falls, I dream that unlikely dream
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.97,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite a full moon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:16.35,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But still lighting up the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:20.23,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become a constellation with you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:24.53,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,The kind that puts out many-colored light
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:28.90,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let these lines \Nthat link us come undone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:34.16,Songs_Insert,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how brightly you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:23.67,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I wasn't going to\Nsay anything before our last song,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.80,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but please let me say one thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:30.67,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much for having us today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.17,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna try our best \Nto become so good,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:36.51,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,that one day you'll brag \Nabout having seen us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:37.56,Default,Girl Student 1,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.14,Default,Girl Student 2,0000,0000,0000,,Budokan-bound!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.98,Default,Boy Student C,0000,0000,0000,,You were great, Whatever-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.65,Default,Girl Student 3,0000,0000,0000,,You did good\Neven when your string broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.69,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.07,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've gotta say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:58.37,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,P-People with social anxiety can't talk \Nwithout a pre-arranged script!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:01.37,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\bord1.5\c&H448CB7&\3c&H000000&\frz341\pos(561,108)}Go! Go!\N{\c&H554A95&}Hitori
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.37,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If you put me in this unplanned situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:07.18,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Say something funny. Something funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:11.13,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Something... Something... funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.17,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.23,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\fnArial Black\frz25.11\c&H858782&\pos(366,237.5)}Kessoku Band
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.61,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.16,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Bocchi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.16,DefaultTop,CF Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Someone call a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:40.06,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You're a legendary rock star!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.29,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.87,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,At least show a little concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:44.96,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.63,Default,CF Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Someone bring a stretcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.63,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori! You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.96,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.71,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.22,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.27,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.98,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Are you conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.48,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.65,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.94,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it wasn't too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:13.61,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:18.12,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry I ruined everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.28,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,After all you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.62,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think people liked it even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.75,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.38,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,They're cleaning up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:31.75,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,They said we'd have an after-party \Nif you were feeling well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.88,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But if you aren't, we can save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.34,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:37.22,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:41.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-san. You got so good so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.64,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Only for rhythm, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.19,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:53.94,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do the kind of playing \Nthat really draws people in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:59.32,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But I seem to be pretty good \Nat the give-and-take with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.83,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna keep working on my playing, \Nso please keep teaching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.12,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.16,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.17,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.71,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.34,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Come by when you're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.46,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:31.31,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become good enough \Nto support Hitori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:39.11,DefaultItalicsTop,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,The 31st Annual Shuka High School \NCulture Festival will now come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.23,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,After-party! After-party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.19,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Bocchi-chan's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.24,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H121512&\b0\fs18\frz350.2\fax-0.08\pos(431.419,174.177)}Area ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.24,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H121512&\b0\fs18\pos(583.958,197.514)\frz345.4\fax-0.1}off limits
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.33,Default,Boy Student D,0000,0000,0000,,Bro look, it's carti.. 🥶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.42,Default,Boy Student E,0000,0000,0000,,Bruh, ur right lmao
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Some day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:01.93,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Some day, I {\i0}will{\i1} gtfo of high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.01,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.81,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:14.31,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I broke the guitar Dad lent me \Nwhile we were playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:17.86,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please, get up! I'm really not mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:18.40,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.40,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a broken peg, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.30,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,It's really not that big a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.24,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:28.70,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it was pretty rad the way \Nyou broke it in the middle of the concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:32.08,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays, they sell guitars \Ndesigned to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.79,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,You should use one of those in your next gig!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.29,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of daughter \Nare you trying to raise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:41.05,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this is probably a good opportunity \Nfor you to buy your own guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.05,DefaultTop,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Play with me, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.51,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.85,DefaultTop,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:46.97,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,That way, if you hit an issue like this again, \Nyou can deal with it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:51.81,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But... Even though I do have a job, \Nall the money goes to my quotas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.10,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.44,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,No worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.73,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,You've got money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:00.28,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where'd it all come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.32,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, are you involved \Nin some crack dealings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.16,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I c-can't accept your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.20,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,We're not {\i1}that{\i0} badly off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:12.71,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's money you earned from \Nadvertisements on your videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:17.04,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,See, if a video gets enough views, \Nthey pay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:22.38,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget the video site account \Nyou use is a family account?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.93,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, my videos...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.55,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,We know all about 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:27.93,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,guitarhero, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:33.14,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,They've been racking up the views, \Nso I monetized 'em in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.81,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,How'd my girl get so good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:40.15,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd need the money eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.10,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,And it's been amazing \Nto see you work so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:47.12,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,and get better and better at the guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.70,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Right, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:49.37,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.95,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about music,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.00,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,but I do think you're amazing at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.46,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... Mom...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.46,0:13:03.88,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,guitarhero
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.46,0:13:03.88,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,This song's been a big hit
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.46,0:13:03.88,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,with all my friends lately!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.46,0:13:03.88,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I sing this all the time at karaoke!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.46,0:13:03.88,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,The chorus gets everyone sooo hype!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.46,0:13:03.88,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,o(^v^)o
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.46,0:13:03.88,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend loves this song!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.51,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's balanced out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:03.92,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,by my sadness at seeing you \Nget better and better at lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.22,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Barf!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:10.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,There's 300,000 yen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:15.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined getting such a windfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:19.90,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If I buy a guitar that costs 100k, \NI'll have 200k left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And if I put that all to quota costs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I could play for almost two years \Nwithout having to work a normal job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.53,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.95,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally quitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:35.29,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan's been unusually chipper today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.92,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,And she bows at me \Nevery time we make eye contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:47.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The thought of quitting my job fills me \Nwith a mysterious and overwhelming power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.89,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Time to talk to the manager now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.14,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra super Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.06,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.48,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I... W-Well... S-See...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:02.23,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll continue to work my hardest \Nand most earnestly at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.36,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the sudden \Ndeclaration of commitment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:08.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing harder than \Ndeclaring you're gonna quit a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.11,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should ghost them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:13.58,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But they do know where I li—\NUh, I mean, I don't want to put them out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to the\Nmusic shop today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:21.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if I buy an instrument \Nfor the manager, she'll let me quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've got lots of money now, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:28.22,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... Could you ask the manager \Nif there's anything she wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:30.22,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan asked that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:33.35,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Since your birthday's coming up, \Nmaybe she's talking about a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.60,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:37.23,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She says no thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.14,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:42.98,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi. I'd like a Dingwall and new Le Fay \Nheadless and a Darkglass amp head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.78,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to the music shop, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's la go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.24,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.24,DefaultTop,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.49,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,But I prefer my presents to be a surprise.
