Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna buy an instrument, \Nyou gotta go to Ochanomizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.54,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:03.38,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why there are \Nso many music shops here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.25,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.83,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,The music business flourished here \Ndue to it playing host in the Meiji Period
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:10.87,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,to Japan's oldest professional orchestra, \Nleading to the formation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:13.92,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,of now-legacy stores in Ochanomizu \Nlike Shimokura Music,
