Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:38.01,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:41.01,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The Season 2 will be on...
